outputs.output_descr: To support Somalis in achieving their full economic potential, Somalia needs an enabling policy, legal and regulatory environment that is stable and transparent and that supports private–sector initiative. UNDP will, in collaboration with other specialized institutions, support such an environment by capitalizing on previous private-sector initiatives implemented by donors/organizations, in particular through the PSG4 (Economic Foundations) working groups.
